code provided by
http://xc3sprog.sourceforge.net/
as needed for FW upload via USB programmer and JTAG for USB3 controllers 
during HW initialisation

the linux sub-directory refers to the xc3sprog svn repo; see details there

The windows directory contains binaries ready for execution. They make use 
of libusb, thus you JTAG programmer should be set up with zadig similar to 
the USBpix system (see wiki instructions)

make sure the executable (both linux and windows) are referred to by the 
PATH environment variable
